          <title>No. 5 Georgia knocks off No. 1 Texas 30-15, with Etienne running for 3 TDs</title>
          <description><![CDATA[AUSTIN, Texas (AP) — Trevor Etienne ran for three touchdowns, the first two set up by cornerback Daylen Everette's takeaways, and fifth-ranked Georgia went on to beat Quinn Ewers and No. 1 Texas 30-15 on Saturday night. Etienne's last score was a 1-yard plunge on fourth down with 12:04 left.]]></description>
